<view class="container">
  <view class="form-header">
    <view class="header-title">委托店铺转让</view>
    <view class="header-desc">提交店铺情况后，平台先做人工审核，再决定公开展示或定向撮合。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="form-body">
    <view class="card hint-card">
      校园店铺转让通常受合同和校方准入限制影响。请尽量填写真实信息，顾问会先协助核对可转让条件。
    </view>

    <view class="card form-card">
      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label flex align-center"><text class="required-star">*</text>联系人称呼</view>
        <input class="item-input" type="text" placeholder="例如：张老板" bindinput="onInputName" value="{{name}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label flex align-center"><text class="required-star">*</text>联系电话</view>
        <input class="item-input" type="number" maxlength="11" placeholder="用于顾问联系核实" bindinput="onInputPhone" value="{{phone}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label flex align-center"><text class="required-star">*</text>店铺位置</view>
        <input class="item-input" type="text" placeholder="学校/校区/食堂或商业街位置" bindinput="onInputLocation" value="{{locationText}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label flex align-center"><text class="required-star">*</text>当前业态</view>
        <input class="item-input" type="text" placeholder="例如：轻食、奶茶、粉面、小吃" bindinput="onInputBusiness" value="{{businessType}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label">面积与费用</view>
        <input class="item-input" type="text" placeholder="例如：45㎡，月租 9000 元，管理费另计" bindinput="onInputFee" value="{{feeText}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label">转让费预期</view>
        <input class="item-input" type="text" placeholder="例如：6 万元，可谈" bindinput="onInputTransferFee" value="{{transferFee}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label">剩余合同期</view>
        <input class="item-input" type="text" placeholder="例如：剩余 18 个月，是否可续约" bindinput="onInputTerm" value="{{remainingTerm}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="item-label">是否含设备</view>
        <radio-group class="experience-group flex align-center" bindchange="onEquipmentIncludedChange">
          <label class="radio-label flex align-center">
            <radio value="true" checked="{{includesEquipment === true}}" color="#3b82f6" />
            <text class="radio-text">含设备</text>
          </label>
          <label class="radio-label flex align-center" style="margin-left: 60rpx;">
            <radio value="false" checked="{{includesEquipment === false}}" color="#3b82f6" />
            <text class="radio-text">不含/待定</text>
          </label>
        </radio-group>
      </view>

      <view class="form-item border-none">
        <view class="item-label">补充说明</view>
        <textarea class="item-textarea" placeholder="可填写流水区间、装修情况、校方是否允许转让、希望保密的信息等"
                  bindinput="onInputRemark" value="{{remark}}" maxlength="300" />
        <view class="char-count">{{remark.length}}/300</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <button class="btn btn-primary submit-btn" bindtap="onSubmitForm" disabled="{{submitting}}">
      {{submitting ? '提交中...' : '提交委托转让'}}
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
